  "prompt": "Where can I buy funky birthday gifts within Rs. 2000?",
  "response": "Looking for funky birthday gifts under Rs. 2000? Here are some great places and ideas where you can find unique and trendy gift options:\n\n### **Online Platforms:**\n1. **Amazon India**: They have a wide range of quirky and funky items like mugs, lamps, personalized gifts, and gadgets.\n   - [www.amazon.in](https://www.amazon.in)\n   \n2. **Flipkart**: Offers funky stationery, quirky home decor, and personalized gifts.\n   - [www.flipkart.com](https://www.flipkart.com)\n   \n3. **Etsy India**: Great for handmade, quirky, and personalized gifts like custom jewelry, wall art, or unique accessories.\n   - [www.etsy.com/in](https://www.etsy.com/in)\n   \n4. **Craftsvilla**: Check out their quirky gifts section for funky items like funky socks, coasters, and decor.\n   - [www.craftsvilla.com](https://www.craftsvilla.com)\n   \n5. **FirstCry**: Not just for kids, they have funky party accessories, quirky stationery, and more.\n   - [www.firstcry.com](https://www.firstcry.com)\n\n6. **Purple Turtle Store**: Known for quirky and funky items like quirky mugs, lamps, and wall decor.\n   - [www.purpleturtlestore.com](https://www.purpleturtlestore.com)\n\n7. **The Souled Store**: Offers funky themed t-shirts, accessories, and home decor items.\n   - [www.thesouledstore.com](https://www.thesouledstore.com)\n\n### **Offline Stores:**\n1. **Chumbak**: Known for quirky and funky home decor, accessories, and stationery. You can find stores in major cities or shop online.\n   \n2. **Archies/Gifts & Greetings**: Great for funky cards, mugs, photo frames, and small decor items.\n   \n3. **Bombay Shirt Company**: Offers quirky and funky accessories like ties, pocket squares, and socks.\n\n4. **Local Markets**: Check out flea markets or local bazaars in your city for unique and handmade quirky items.\n\n### **Funky Gift Ideas Under Rs. 2000:**\n- **Personalized Customized Gifts** (mugs, cushions, photo frames)\n- **Quirky Socks or Ties**\n- **Funky Lamps or LED Lights**\n- **Mini Desk Toys or Stress Relievers**\n- **Themed T-Shirts**\n- **Unique Keychains or Accessories**\n- **Fun Board Games or Puzzles**\n- **Planters or Succulent Pots**\n- **Funky Journals or Notebooks**\n- **Retro Posters or Wall Art**\n\nThese options should help you find something fun and unique within your budget!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
